flavor_text_entries.gold:
The BERRIES it
stores in its
vase-like shell decompose and
become a gooey
liquid.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
It stores BERRIES
inside its shell.
To avoid attacks, it hides beneath
rocks and remains
completely still.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
The fluid secreted
by its toes carves
holes in rocks for nesting and can be
mixed with BERRIES
to make a drink.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
SHUCKLE quietly hides itself under
rocks, keeping its body concealed
inside its hard shell while eating berries it has stored away.
The berries mix with its body fluids to
become a juice.
